<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>VATrix</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --font-primary: 'Afacad', sans-serif;
      --font-secondary: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      --color-white: #ffffff;
      --color-black: #000000;
      --color-accent: #0092D3;
      --bg-dark: #000000;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: var(--font-secondary);
      background-color: var(--bg-dark);
      color: var(--color-white);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* Navbar */
    .navbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background-color: var(--color-black);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      animation: slideIn 1s ease-out;
    }

    .navbar .logo {
      font-family: var(--font-primary);
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      animation: heartbeat 1.5s ease-in-out 3;
    }

    .navbar .tagline {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--color-white);
    }

    /* Main Section */
    .main-container {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .intro {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .quote {
      font-family: var(--font-primary);
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-out forwards 1s;
    }

    .description {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* Projects Section */
    .projects {
      margin-top: 50px;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease-out forwards 1s;
    }

    .projects h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-left: 10px;
    }

    .project-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      width: 90%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards 1s;
    }

    .project-card img {
      width: 45%;
      max-height: 250px;
      object-fit: contain;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .project-details {
      max-width: 50%;
      text-align: left;
      margin-left: 50px;
    }

    .project-details h3 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .project-details p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .learn-more {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--color-white);
      background-color: var(--color-accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .learn-more:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      background-color: var(--color-white);
      color: var(--color-black);
    }

    /* Social Media Section */
    .social {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 50px;
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards 1s;
    }

    .social h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .social-icons {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .social-icons a {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      background-color: var(--color-accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--color-white);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .social-icons a:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      background-color: var(--color-white);
      color: var(--color-black);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .project-card {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .project-card img {
        width: 70%;
        max-height: 200px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .project-details {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .social-icons a {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }
    }

    .form-container {
      margin-top: 30px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      padding: 50px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease-out forwards 3s;
    }

    .form-container h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: var(--color-accent);
    }

    .form-container form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .form-container label {
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .form-container input,
    .form-container textarea {
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      color: var(--color-black);
    }

    .form-container input:focus,
    .form-container textarea:focus {
      outline: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    }

    .form-container button {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      background-color: var(--color-accent);
      color: var(--color-white);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .form-container button:hover {
      background-color: var(--color-white);
      color: var(--color-black);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .form-container {
        width: 90%;
      }
    }

     /* Section Styling */
     .main-container {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .section {
        margin: 50px auto;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 40px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        width: 90%;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
        width: 90%;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .section p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      max-width: 70%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Animations */
    @keyframes slideIn {
      from {
        transform: translateX(-100%);
      }
      to {
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes heartbeat {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: scale(1);
      }
      25% {
        transform: scale(1.1);
      }
      50% {
        transform: scale(1.2);
      }
      75% {
        transform: scale(1.1);
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">VATrix</div>
    <div class="tagline">Vision AI & Tech Robotics</div>
  </header>

  <div class="main-container">
    <section class="intro">
      <blockquote class="quote">“Where Machines See, Think and Act”</blockquote>
      <p class="description">
        We create advanced AI-powered robots designed for safety, security, and real-life guardianship. 
        Specializing in robotic arms and autonomous systems, our vision combines cutting-edge technology 
        with intelligent solutions to redefine protection.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="projects">
      <h2>Our Projects</h2>
      <div class="project-card">
        
        <div class="project-details">
          <h3>Nirva-Agni</h3>
          <p>
            NIRVA-AGNI is an AI-based fire extinguishing robotic arm which detects and extinguishes 
            fires in real-time. It provides 24/7 fire protection, improves safety, reduces damage, and 
            requires minimal human intervention.
          </p>
          <a href="/index" class="learn-more">Learn More</a>
        </div>
        <img src="\Nirvaagni.png" alt="Nirva-Agni Project">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="social">
      <h3>Stay updated on</h3>
      <div class="social-icons">
        <a href="#" title="YouTube">&#x1F4FA;</a>
        <a href="#" title="LinkedIn">&#x1F465;</a>
        <a href="#" title="Instagram">&#x1F4F7;</a>
        <a href="#" title="Twitter">&#x1F426;</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          To create a world where technology serves as a catalyst for safety and innovation. 
          Through AI-powered robotics and advanced automation, we strive to redefine protection, 
          improve lives, and inspire global progress in the fields of security and technology.
        </p>
      </section>
  
      <!-- Contact Form Section -->
      <section class="form-container">
        <h3>Get in Touch with Us</h3>
        <form action="#" method="POST">
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
          
          <label for="mobile">Mobile</label>
          <input type="tel" id="mobile" name="mobile" placeholder="Your Mobile Number" required>
          
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
          
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
          
          <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </form>
      </section>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
